{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 57704, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 9734, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re : 像老年人学习", "timestamp": 1593332089, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 57710, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 9734, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "首先 逼着自己早睡", "timestamp": 1593332174, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 57715, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 9734, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "然后定闹铃逼着自己在某个时间起床 就算前一天在床上实际上躺了四五个小时睡不着 起床以后灌点咖啡", "timestamp": 1593332213, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 57719, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 9734, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 不如让父母强制拉闸(*^_^*)", "timestamp": 1593332232, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 57725, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 9734, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 谢谢!", "timestamp": 1593332264, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 57726, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 9734, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "一整天撑着不睡 就算一天困得什么都做不进去也不睡 然后晚上依旧按前一天时间早睡 这样过两天就好了", "timestamp": 1593332266, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 57754, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 9734, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "我用褪黑素调了三天之后 自己到这个点也能睡着了（我以前我从来没用过褪黑素）\n之后就保持早睡早起而且每天锻炼1h 效果超棒 我已经最少凌晨两点睡后一年半多了2333", "timestamp": 1593332458, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 57821, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 9734, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "我有两天怎么也睡不着，第三天喜提健康作息", "timestamp": 1593333002, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 57893, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 9734, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Carol: 褪黑素这个会不会对身体有啥不好的影响啊，怎么知道用量呢", "timestamp": 1593333671, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 58156, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 9734, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "根据我查的资料和问别人，短期是没啥问题的，我自己也是吃了三天就停了。剂量是3mg，想睡前吃一颗。\n我觉得重点就是短期，最好别长期吃。然后前提是你真的想改作息，锻炼锻炼逼自己，后面就会调整过来滴 加油～", "timestamp": 1593336167, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "likenum": 3, "pid": 9734, "reply": 10, "tag": null, "text": "大家有没有什么调整作息的好方法啊", "timestamp": 1593332058, "type": "text", "updated_at": 1606782585, "url": "", "vote": {}}}